{"type":"message","id":"09cb9131","parentId":"e6a7428b","timestamp":"2026-05-21T01:00:00.129Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Thursday, May 21st, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-05-21 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1779325200127}}
{"type":"message","id":"b83a81ce","parentId":"09cb9131","timestamp":"2026-05-21T01:04:21.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job that fires at 9:00 AM Asia/Shanghai every day to refresh the Cursor collaboration rules. The message says to silently confirm - no reply needed, just acknowledge internally and return a plain text summary.\n\nLet me just return a brief confirmation."},{"type":"text","text":"Cursor 协作规则已确认：\n1. 任务提交用 `submit_task.py --title --instructions --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify`\n2. 用户回复确认用 `confirm_write.py --task-id --decision auto --reply \"原文\"`\n3. 查看队列：`--list`\n4. 查看结果：`--results`\n\n规则已熟记，静默确认完成。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779325200128}}
